ü§ñ Here what's coming in the next Telegram update (__v12.1.0__):

‚Äî Design Liquid Glass in Telegram iOS. 
[[View 1](https://t.me/telelakel/631?single)]

‚Äî Removing gift Description.
You can delete description from gifts, but it costs 1000 Stars. If the gift is on the blockchain, you won‚Äôt be able to remove its caption.
[[View 1](https://t.me/telelakel/632)], [[View 2](https://t.me/telelakel/647)].

‚Äî Premium gifts now show how many of them a user can buy.
[[View 1](https://t.me/telelakel/633)]

‚Äî When a gift was given, transferred, or purchased.
Above each gift, you can see the date and who gave, transferred, or bought it for you. Only you can see this.
[[View 1](https://t.me/telelakel/633)], [[View 2](https://t.me/telelakel/646)].

‚Äî Detailed information about a gift when transferring it to another user.
When you transfer a gift, you‚Äôll see details like its model, background, and pattern.
[[View 1](https://t.me/telelakel/634)], [[View 2](https://t.me/telelakel/649)].

‚Äî Text chat in voice chats for channels/groups and in group calls.
You can now leave short messages or reactions in voice chats and group calls. Each message stays visible for about 10 seconds.
This feature isn‚Äôt available in streams.
Also redesigned on iOS with the new Liquid Glass style.
[[View 1](https://t.me/telelakel/635)], [[View 2](https://t.me/telelakel/648)].

‚Äî Note on a user.
If the user is in your contacts, you can add a personal note to them. Only you will see it. To add one, just tap Edit Contact.
[[View 1](https://t.me/telelakel/636)], [[View 2](https://t.me/telelakel/643)].

‚Äî Suggest Date of Birth for a contact.
If your contact hasn‚Äôt set a birthday, you can suggest one for them (__Why this exists, I honestly have no idea__).
[[View 1](https://t.me/telelakel/637)], [[View 2](https://t.me/telelakel/644)]

‚Äî Upgrade Gifts Timer.
It shows how many hours/minutes/seconds are left until the upgrade price changes. There‚Äôs also a button that gives you detailed info about the drop ‚Äî the time, date, and the new price after it decreases.
[[View 1](https://t.me/telelakel/639)]

‚Äî You be able to add gifts to your profile that have been sent to the blockchain.
[[View 1](https://t.me/telelakel/640)], [[View 2](https://t.me/telelakel/645)].

‚Äî Try on a gift as your profile background before buying it. 
You can also purchase it right away ‚Äî a button with the price will appear at the bottom.
[[View 1](https://t.me/telelakel/641)], [[View 2](https://t.me/telelakel/650)].

‚Äî Set a gift as the background for your name.
You can use a gift you already own, or try one on and buy it right away from Telegram internal market.
**!!!** Available only for Westside Sign, Mighty Arm, Heroic Helmet, and Nail Bracelet gifts.
[[View 1](https://t.me/telelakel/642)], [[View 2](https://t.me/telelakel/651)].

__This list is meant to provide detailed info and may be updated if new features are added.__ __This update applies to iOS and Android devices. Others will follow later.__
